    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, so it's looking flawless and drives like a dream. If you're looking for something that's been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
