      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish is breathtaking, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero imperfections, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creasing, while the high-gloss wood trim retains its factory brilliance. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy, documented by a comprehensive binder of service records from authorized specialists. With a whisper-quiet engine and a transmission that shifts with seamless grace, this is a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of a modern classic. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
